Hello after a few months gone and then deleting my profile i am back! I'll be slowly uploading just about all my old TI here and all the new ones i made as well.

This is a Textual Inversion so place it in your embedding folder. I know its a Bin file but it works just the same. I have no control over it.

Have Fun Be Kind
